Global Pyrroloquinoline Quinone Disodium (PQQ) Salt Market Insights
Pyrroloquinoline Quinone Disodium (PQQ) Salt Market size was valued at USD 0.35 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 0.70 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 9.2% from 2024 to 2030.

Pyrroloquinoline Quinone Disodium (PQQ) Salt Market Overview
The global Pyrroloquinoline Quinone Disodium (PQQ) Salt market is valued at approximately USD 50 million in 2024 and is expected to witness steady growth over the next decade. This market growth is fueled by rising awareness of PQQ's health benefits, including its antioxidant properties, role in mitochondrial health, and potential in neuroprotection. In addition, increasing demand from the dietary supplement industry is contributing to the expansion of this market. The market is also supported by advancements in production technologies and rising applications in pharmaceuticals and food products.

